snippet.title: Resistance 204X Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Designed to introduce new players into fighting games, Resistance 204X, is a fast-paced footsies-based 2D indie fighting game currently in development for PC and Mobile.

Choose your character and fight against other players locally or cross-play online.

Rollback Netcode.
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1829140/Resistance_204X/
Free early access at https://resistance204x.com
